			<h3 ><a href="#p17812" rel="nofollow"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Re: Pick The Year This Deal Becomes A Bad Contract<!-- google_ad_section_end --></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=17812&amp;sid=e4217d8a8df5d8a2ba82218c898d18f6#p17812"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=17812&amp;sid=e4217d8a8df5d8a2ba82218c898d18f6#p17812" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#6</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=179&amp;sid=e4217d8a8df5d8a2ba82218c898d18f6" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">ofahn</a></strong> &raquo; December 26th, 2012, 4:52 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

